data.description: This Beautiful updated 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located on a freshwater canal with access to the Gulf of Mexico in beautiful Hernando Beach, FL. Has a new metal roof, new stainless steel refrigerator, and stove. If you enjoy Boating, Kayaking, Fishing, and being surrounded by wildlife, or just sitting on the dock relaxing this is the place for you. There is tile throughout the main living area, the kitchen has stainless steel appliances, the master bedroom has a large walk-in closet and en suite, there is also a deck off the master BR perfect for enjoying the amazing sunsets, there are Vaulted ceiling in the Family/ dining room, there is a large 2nd bedroom and bathroom large deck on the back of house Flood Zone is AE so low-cost flood insurance. This home is Close to shopping, restaurants, beaches, parks, Golf courses, and so much more. This home is a must-see.
